                            <comment id="13850856" author="jmspaggi" created="Tue, 17 Dec 2013 20:26:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My bad, sorry.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have added some output logs into bin/hbase but rolling_restart and others are calling it to get zk information, and are parsing the result. So they was taking my output logs as ZK info, and failed. Removing the output from bin/hbase fixed the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
